summary.span: 提供自訂資料的字串給提供者做為設定檔屬性。

span.span: Provides a string of custom data to the provider for a profile property.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 類別用來提供具有自訂設定檔提供者的設定檔內容的資料字串。The class is used to supply a string of data with a profile property to a custom profile provider. 自訂資料字串可以設定為任何字串值，並使用設定`customProviderData`可加入設定檔屬性的組態項目的屬性。The custom data string can be set to any string value and is set using the `customProviderData` attribute of the configuration element for adding profile properties. 如果`customProviderData`設定屬性，則值會置於屬性的集合和編製索引的名稱"CustomProviderData。 」If the `customProviderData` attribute is set, then the value is placed in the collection for the property and is indexed by the name "CustomProviderData."
